?\u201d"},{"bookname":"John","chapter":"8","verse":"49","text":"Jesus answered, \u201cI am not possessed by a demon, but I honor my Father – and yet you dishonor me."},{"bookname":"John","chapter":"8","verse":"50","text":"I am not trying to get praise for myself. There is one who demands it, and he also judges."},{"bookname":"John","chapter":"8","verse":"51","text":"I tell you the solemn truth, if anyone obeys my teaching, he will never see death.\u201d<\/p>"},{"bookname":"John","chapter":"8","verse":"52","text":" Then the Judeans responded, \u201cNow we know you\u2019re possessed by a demon! Both Abraham and the prophets died, and yet you say, \u2018If anyone obeys my teaching, he will never experience death.\u2019"},{"bookname":"John","chapter":"8","verse":"53","text":"You aren\u2019t greater than our father Abraham who died, are you? And the prophets died too! Who do you claim to be?\u201d"},{"bookname":"John","chapter":"8","verse":"54","text":"Jesus replied, \u201cIf I glorify myself, my glory is worthless. The one who glorifies me is my Father, about whom you people say, \u2018He is our God.\u2019"},{"bookname":"John","chapter":"8","verse":"55","text":"Yet you do not know him, but I know him. If I were to say that I do not know him, I would be a liar like you. But I do know him, and I obey his teaching."},{"bookname":"John","chapter":"8","verse":"56","text":"Your father Abraham was overjoyed to see my day, and he saw it and was glad.\u201d<\/p>"},{"bookname":"John","chapter":"8","verse":"57","text":" Then the Judeans replied, \u201cYou are not yet fifty years old! Have you seen Abraham?\u201d"},{"bookname":"John","chapter":"8","verse":"58","text":"Jesus said to them, \u201cI tell you the solemn truth, before Abraham came into existence, I am!\u201d"},{"bookname":"John","chapter":"8","verse":"59","text":"Then they picked up stones to throw at him, but Jesus hid himself and went out from the temple area.<\/p>"},{"bookname":"John","chapter":"9","verse":"1","text":