if he has fallen asleep, he will recover.\u201d"},{"bookname":"John","chapter":"11","verse":"13","text":"(Now Jesus had been talking about his death, but they thought he had been talking about real sleep.)<\/p>"},{"bookname":"John","chapter":"11","verse":"14","text":" Then Jesus told them plainly, \u201cLazarus has died,"},{"bookname":"John","chapter":"11","verse":"15","text":"and I am glad for your sake that I was not there, so that you may believe. But let us go to him.\u201d"},{"bookname":"John","chapter":"11","verse":"16","text":"So Thomas (called Didymus) said to his fellow disciples, \u201cLet us go too, so that we may die with him.\u201d<\/p>"},{"bookname":"John","chapter":"11","verse":"17","text":" When Jesus arrived, he found that Lazarus had been in the tomb four days already."},{"bookname":"John","chapter":"11","verse":"18","text":"(Now Bethany was less than two miles from Jerusalem,"},{"bookname":"John","chapter":"11","verse":"19","text":"so many of the Jewish people of the region had come to Martha and Mary to console them over the loss of their brother.)"},{"bookname":"John","chapter":"11","verse":"20","text":"So when Martha heard that Jesus was coming, she went out to meet him, but Mary was sitting in the house."},{"bookname":"John","chapter":"11","verse":"21","text":"Martha said to Jesus, \u201cLord, if you had been here, my brother would not have died."},{"bookname":"John","chapter":"11","verse":"22","text":"But even now I know that whatever you ask from God, God will grant you.\u201d<\/p>"},{"bookname":"John","chapter":"11","verse":"23","text":" Jesus replied, \u201cYour brother will come back to life again.\u201d"},{"bookname":"John","chapter":"11","verse":"24","text":"Martha said, \u201cI know that he will come back to life again in the resurrection at the last day.\u201d"},{"bookname":"John","chapter":"11","verse":"25","text":"Jesus said to her, \u201cI am the resurrection and the life. The one who believes in me will live even if he dies,"},{"b